00:40:11.760 --> 00:40:12.950
Alas otso. pangako ko sayo.

00:40:13.720 --> 00:40:14.620
Ibinibigay ko sa iyo ang aking salita.

00:40:14.640 --> 00:40:16.780
Tataas ang sirena ng air raid na iyon.

00:40:49.640 --> 00:40:50.550
Ms. Xian

00:40:51.200 --> 00:40:52.470
